title: Lewisville wins 10-year water quality award from the state (City of Lewisville, TX)
text: ( Source : City of Lewisville, TX ) Texas Commission on Environmental Quality has awarded the Lewisville Water Treatment Plant staff a Texas Optimization Program Award for drinking water quality. The award was presented at the City Council
